title.rendered: Higher, boxset de remezclas de The Horrors

content.rendered:
Un año más tarde de publicar Skying, los británicos de The Horrors han recuperado singles, videos y remezclas para un box set que se pondrá a disposición del público a través de iTunes,  y que además se publicará en formato físico (CD doble, 4 Vinilos de 12″ y un DVD).

Llevará por título Higher y este será su contenido:

CD 1:

  1. I Can See Through You (Blanck Mass Remix)
  2. Monica Gems (Daniel Avery Remix)
  3. Still Life (Connan Mockasin Remix)
  4. You Said (Peaking Lights Dub U Mix)
  5. Still Life (Still Living Still Giving Cherrystones Remix)
  6. Moving Further Away (Andrew Weatherall Remix)

 

CD 2:

  1. Comes in Waves (Seahawks Skying Suite)
  2. Moving Further Away (Andy Blake World Unknown Mix)
  3. Dive In (The Pressure Ridges)
  4. You Said (JTC Remix)
  5. Wild Eyed (Andrew Weatherall Remix)
  6. Moving Into Blue (Seahawks Skying Suite)

 

12″ (1):

  1. A1 Still Life
  2. A2 Still Life (Connan Mockasin Remix)
  3. B1 Still Life (Still Living Still Giving Cherrystones Remix)
  4. B2 Dive In (The Pressure Ridges) Chris Watson Remix

 

12″ (2):

  1. A1 I Can See Through You
  2. A2 Monica Gems (Daniel Avery Remix)
  3. B1 I Can See Through You (Blanck Mass Remix)

 

12″ (3):

  1. A1 Changing the Rain
  2. A2 You Said (Peaking Lights Dub U Mix)
  3. B1 Comes in Waves (Seahawks Skying Suite)

 

12″ (4):

  1. A1 Moving Further Away (Andrew Weatherall Remix)
  2. B1 Moving Further Away (Andy Blake World Unknown Mix)

 

DVD:

  1. Still Life
  2. I Can See Through You
  3. Change the Rain
